title: For Sale:  The USP45 listed is NOT A USP45CT
postcontent:
Don't know if the guy is pulling a scam or just doesn't know, but the listing in Nashville for a USP45CT is not for a genuine CT. 
ALL compact tacticals (CTs) are rollmarked on the slide "USP CT". The pistol in the guy's pics is rollmarked USP Compact, like every other compact out there. 
Also, the barrel in that pistol is a factory HK replacement. You can tell by the lack of serial number on the barrel on the extractor slide. HK replacement barrels have the SN etched on the opposite side of the barrel, hidden by the slide.
This pistol is a regular USP45 Compact with an added threaded barrel.
DO NOT GET SCAMMED!!!
